          <span class="font-medium">Written Warranties</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <!-- Main Content Column -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Concrete Driveway Services in Port Orange & Volusia County</h2>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600">
            <p>Your driveway is one of the first things people notice about your home. A cracked, stained, or deteriorating driveway can detract from your property's appearance and even affect its value. At Port Orange Concrete Co., we specialize in creating beautiful, functional concrete driveways that enhance your home's curb appeal while providing decades of reliable service.</p>
            
            <p>Whether you need a brand new driveway installation, want to extend your existing driveway for additional parking, or need to repair and resurface worn concrete, our experienced team has the skills and equipment to deliver exceptional results. We've been serving homeowners throughout Volusia County for over 40 years, and our reputation for quality work and honest service has made us the area's most trusted concrete contractor.</p>
            
